     "message": "Webex Engineering has planned a maintenance window to support ongoing service maintenance and system upgrades.\n\n<strong>-- Affected Data Centers --</strong>\nCanada, Chicago, and Texas\n\n<strong>-- Scheduled Maintenance Window --</strong>\nStart: Friday, July 17, 2026, 03:00 UTC\nComplete: Friday, July 17, 2026, 08:00 UTC\n\n<strong>-- Affected Services --</strong>\nWebex Calling / Webex Calling Wholesale / Cisco BroadCloud\n \n<strong>-- User Experience --</strong>\nDuring the Webex Calling Application Server maintenance, Control Hub, Rialto Market Portal, and programmatic Provisioning interfaces (Rialto API) may be temporarily unavailable for the duration of the maintenance window.\n\nWholesale customer and user provisioning will be impacted.\n\nCall processing is expected to remain unaffected.\n\nPlans for this maintenance are subject to change. This notice will be updated at https://status.webex.com during the maintenance period.\n\nFor help and support, visit our website at https://help.webex.com.\n\nThank you for your patience as we continue to improve the Webex services.",
